column1: This was my first attempt at being a meet director. The meet was a huge success for me and the Rapid City YMCA.
So many more spectators showed up than expected! We had 34 lifters. Steve Howard (SD State USAPL Chair) was a
tremendous help and support. Lifters came for SD, WY, MN and NE. Looking forward to doing the meet on 2004!
Open: Can be any age.               Junior: up to 23 (Dec 31)
